&lt;p&gt;Centria Healthcare is hiring compassionate &lt;strong&gt;Registered Nurses (RNs) and Licensed Practical Nurses (LPNs)&lt;/strong&gt; to provide &lt;strong&gt;1:1 private duty nursing&lt;/strong&gt; in patients’ homes. You’ll deliver skilled, personalized care to pediatric and adult patients in a low-stress, relationship-based setting.&lt;/p&gt;
