&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4&quot;&gt;Our client is a 63 year old man who was in a motor vehicle accident in the 90&#39;s. Currently he is in hospice and bed-bound. He lives in a clean, smoke free home with his wife and 3 cats in Mt Pleasant.&amp;nbsp;He is a fan of sports, enjoys watching tv and playing games like solitaire, tic tac toe, and word searches.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
