&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;5,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;5,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Safety Precautions:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;His medical status puts him at high risk for an adrenal crisis, particularly from stressors like infection.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
