&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;7,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;7,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Supportive Family:&lt;/strong&gt; The client’s wife is known for being exceptionally kind and easy to work with, fostering a respectful professional atmosphere.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;7,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;7,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Environment: &lt;/strong&gt;Very neat and clean home&lt;/li&gt;
